FIFA International Soccer CD³²:

        Here are some codes for this great soccer game.  All codes must be
        entered with the joybad in the Options mode.  If a code does not
        work exit the options menu, re-enter and try again.  The 'L' and
        'R' are the buttons on top of the joypad.

                    Y Y Y X A A A B      -Invisible Walls
                    X A B Y Y B A X      -Crazy Ball
                    B A R B Y L          -Curve Ball
                    B A B B B B B B B B  -Super Kicks
                    A A A A A Y Y Y Y Y  -Super Goalie
                    A A B B Y Y X X      -Dream Team
                    L L L L L R L        -Super Defence
                    R R R R R L R        -Super Offence
